    "description": "故事开始于恩迦迪亚大陆。故事的主人公艾罗哈特踏上了一场旅程，意在阻止自己亲生哥哥的邪恶计划——释放世代囚禁于暗影中的古老邪恶，用德拉伊德石的力量发动战争。  <br><br>你能直面自己的哥哥，阻止他执行邪恶计划么？ <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>投身即时战斗  <br>以即时战斗的方式与凶恶的怪物搏斗。投掷炸弹，施放法术，饮用药水，渡过恩迦迪亚大陆的重重难关。  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493940/extras/d3cf6e82806bbffd37e0e252fa56f909.poster.avif?t=1751535320\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493940/extras/d3cf6e82806bbffd37e0e252fa56f909.webm?t=1751535320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493940/extras/d3cf6e82806bbffd37e0e252fa56f909.mp4?t=1751535320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>游览引人入胜的开放世界  <br>探索复古风格的美丽俯视角像素世界，回到经典游戏的时代。畅游广阔而引人入胜的世界，结识各色人物，领略风土人情。  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493940/extras/539d8f51e15617895900af3da44e6e75.poster.avif?t=1751535320\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493940/extras/539d8f51e15617895900af3da44e6e75.webm?t=1751535320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493940/extras/539d8f51e15617895900af3da44e6e75.mp4?t=1751535320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>征服地城，解开谜题  <br>获取武器和盔甲，学习魔法能力来解开复杂的谜题，解锁新地区以供探索。探索阴暗的地城，躲避致命的陷阱，打败凶恶的敌人。  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493940/extras/b45fae2dcfa9961915796105c49c7cae.poster.avif?t=1751535320\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_